        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Ok - I'm sure there will be a review for database passwords.\n > Possibly this will cover topic endpoints, as dmaap is a rest\n > server??\n\nUnfortunately, it will not cover topic endpoints as the REST server component is buried down inside third-party libraries (i.e., DmaapClient and CambriaClient).",
