        "timestamp": "2020-02-17 16:44:42.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n> > Jim - is this going to work?\n > \n > as long as the environment variables make it to the JVM, it seems\n > like this should work, yes.\n\nI think csits will break for components using RestServer, so companion changes would need to go there unless there was a default fallback option to use the parameters per comment below.",
